profile:
Provincial Granicrete is the certified distributor and installer for Granicrete International in Saskatchewan. 

    * Counter Tops - Granite, Marble, Concrete, the possibilities are endless. Virtually any look can be easily achieved in just a couple of days.…
    * Exterior Flooring and Pool Decks – Upgrading your existing driveway, patio or pool deck for a price you can afford.…
    * Interior Flooring – Why settle for the ordinary when you can have the extraordinary. Let your imagination be the limit with our enormous line of flooring for any room in your home.…
    * 3D Structures – Our 3D Structures are the perfect accent for your home or business. Always wanted a pond or waterfall in the backyard? We can do it.…
